spec: asyncio_extra134
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(asyncio)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-sync.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-sync.html — Python asyncio synchronization primitives documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/locks.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: wave 257 theme — asyncio.Semaphore and asyncio.BoundedSemaphore method qualnames and class identity. NEW in extra134: asyncio.Semaphore.__init__.__qualname__=='Semaphore.__init__' (len=18); asyncio.Semaphore.acquire.__qualname__=='Semaphore.acquire' (len=17); asyncio.Semaphore.release.__qualname__=='Semaphore.release' (len=17); asyncio.Semaphore.locked.__qualname__=='Semaphore.locked' (len=16); asyncio.Semaphore.__module__=='asyncio.locks' (len=13); asyncio.Semaphore.__bases__[0].__name__=='_ContextManagerMixin'; asyncio.Semaphore.__mro__.__len__()==4; asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.__init__.__qualname__=='BoundedSemaphore.__init__' (len=25); asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.release.__qualname__=='BoundedSemaphore.release' (len=24); asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.__bases__[0].__name__=='Semaphore'; asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.__mro__.__len__()==5. All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Semaphore.__mro__.__len__() == 4. MRO is [Semaphore, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object]. BoundedSemaphore adds one level: [BoundedSemaphore, Semaphore, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object] (len=5). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.acquire.__qualname__ == 'Semaphore.acquire' (len=17), NOT 'BoundedSemaphore.acquire', because BoundedSemaphore inherits acquire from Semaphore without overriding it. Only release is overridden in BoundedSemaphore. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Semaphore.__init__.__code__.co_argcount == 2 (self + value), while acquire/release/locked all have co_argcount==1 (self only). BoundedSemaphore.__init__.__code__.co_argcount==2 (self + value). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

